==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ταχύ / tachu / takh-oo'
Neuter singular of [[ταχύς]] (as adverb); shortly, that is, without delay, soon, or (by surprise) suddenly, or (by implication of ease) readily

===Adverb===
'''ταχύ'''

# [[lightly]], [[quickly]].

